 <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold uppercase tracking-tight text-charcoal group-hover:text-gold-600">Fleet Uniform Stores</h3>
 <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-ash">Own your uniforms instead of renting. Logo and names on file.</p>
 </a>
 <a href="/blog/how-to-outfit-a-construction-crew-vegas/" class="group border border-hairline bg-panel p-6 transition-colors hover:border-gold-500">
 <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold uppercase tracking-tight text-charcoal group-hover:text-gold-600">Outfitting a Vegas Crew</h3>
 <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-ash">How many shirts, pants, and coveralls per tech — the real math.</p>
